(The dual-port synchronous SRAM\
 is optimized for\
 speed and density.\
 The memory is designed to\
 take full advantage of ) TextPiece

(TSMC) length 0 eq
{
  (the) TextPiece
  ( 90nm CLN90G process.) TextPiece
