TextParaEnd
() TextLine
TextParaStart
(The storage array is composed of eight-transistor\
 bit cells with fully static circuitry. The\
 SRAM\
 operates at a voltage of 0.9V to 1.1V) TextPiece
( and a junction temperature range of ) TextPiece
(-401C) TextReserveSpace
