(CLKA, CLKB) (Port A & B Clocks) Table2LL
(CENA, CENB) (Port A & B Chip Enables) Table2LL
(WENA,WENB) (Port A & B Write Enables \(Active low\)) Table2LL
(QA[31:0], QB[31:0]) 
  (Port A & B Data Outputs \(QA[0],QB[0] = LSB\)) Table2LL
(EMAA[2:0], EMAB[2:0]) 
  (Port A & B Margin Adjustment \(EMAA[0],EMAB[0] = LSB\)) Table2LL
Table2End
